# Assertions consumed by `hastur dagon`. Each non-blank, non-comment line is
# `<file-relative-to-outdir>: <substring>` — the runner checks the substring
# is present in that file.

# --- Project module: signatures + cross-link to system module ---
tdoc_smoke.html: <h1>tdoc_smoke</h1>
tdoc_smoke.html: <code><span class="kw">proc</span> <span class="name">square</span>
tdoc_smoke.html: <code><span class="kw">proc</span> <span class="name">shout</span>
tdoc_smoke.html: <span class="prim">int</span>
tdoc_smoke.html: <a class="typeref" href="std/system.html#string.0.sysvq0asl">
tdoc_smoke.html: id="square.0.
tdoc_smoke.html: id="shout.0.

# --- Module-level markdown rendered ---
tdoc_smoke.html: <h1>Markdown smoke test</h1>
